        "text": "Les ruego, hermanos, por el nombre de nuestro Señor Jesucristo, que hablen todos una misma cosa y que no haya entre ustedes divisiones. Antes, estén perfectamente unidos en una misma mente y un mismo parecer"
      },
      "egwNotes": "I urge our people to cease their criticism and evil-speaking, and go to God in earnest prayer, asking Him to help them to help the erring. Let them link up with one another and with Christ. Let them study the seventeenth of John, and learn how to pray and how to live the prayer of Christ. He is the Comforter. He will abide in their hearts, making their joy full. His words will be to them as the bread of life, and in the strength thus gained they will be enabled to develop characters that will be an honor to God. Perfect Christian fellowship will exist among them. There will be seen in their li...",
